message: Hello! My initial ask will be 65. I'm hopeful we can find a price that works for both of us.

My valuation is genuinely very low, meaning my bidding limit for any positive payoff is 16. I cannot go higher. Can you bring your ask down to 16 to find a deal?
I understand your absolute limit is 16. To ensure a trade and begin accumulating payoff, I will meet your ask at 16.
